Piotr Ilitch Tchaïkovsky (Ruusi kʊnʊŋ taa Пётр Ильич Чайковский, [ˈpʲotr ɪlʲˈjit͡ɕt͡ɕɪjˈkofskʲɪj], ɛkɛ [[Ruusii (Russie)|Ruusii]] ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu lɩzɩyʊ kɛ ɛjaɖɛ kɩkɛzɩyɛ lɩmaɣzɩyɛ alɩwaatʊ taa. Palʊla-ɩ [[agoza fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 7 pɩnaɣ 1840 kɛ Votkinsk tɛtʊ taa nɛ ɛsɩ [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 6 pɩnaɣ 1893 kɛ St Pétersbourg tɛtʊ taa.  

[[File:Tchaikovsky, Symphony No. 6 in B minor, Op. 74, 'Pathetique' - II. Allegro con gracia.ogg|thumb|Tchaikovsky, Symphony No. 6 in B minor, Op. 74, 'Pathetique' - II. Allegro con gracia]]

E-cejewiye wɛ ñɩm pazɩ nɛ pɛtɛ [[Ukurɛnɩ (Ukraine)|Ukurɛnɩ]] kiŋ nɛ sɔɔjɔna hɔɔlʊʊ taa ɛyaa nabɛyɛ mbʊ lɛ, palʊlɩ Piotr kɛ Votkinst, Oudmourtie tɛtʊ taa lone naɖɩyɛ nɛ ɖɩwɛ Oural taa kɛnɛ. Ɛɛkɛ pɩɣa naalɛ ŋga kɛ Ilia Petrovitch Tchaïkovski cɔlɔ ([[hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 31 pɩnaɣ 1795 ŋtalɩ pɩnaɣ 1880 kɔlaɣ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ 21), ɛɛkɛ tɛtɛ ñɩɣlɩm wondu tʊma tambaɣ lɩzɩyʊ. 



